name: rtree
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.8.3" %}

package:
  name: rtree
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: rtree-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/Toblerity/rtree/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ab9d29ea3935d189ce32217ad5f5aff464a7ded9e9f9777e2d8dbf11dcf90b93
  patches:
    - find_libray.patch
    - setup-win.path  # [win]
    - find_libray-win32.patch  # [win32]

build:
  number: 0
  preserve_egg_dir: True
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - libspatialindex
  run:
    - python
    - libspatialindex

test:
  imports:
    - rtree
  commands:
    - conda inspect linkages -p $PREFIX rtree  # [not win]
    - conda inspect objects -p $PREFIX rtree  # [osx]

about:
  home: http://toblerity.github.com/rtree/
  license: LGPL-2.1
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'R-Tree spatial index for Python GIS.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf

about.summary: R-Tree spatial index for Python GIS.
